:19:\"WordPress Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"contact form\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"guest post submission form\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"wpforms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=224078\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:599:\"<p>Are you interested in learning how to create a guest post submission form? Thats a great idea! If you own a blog, but dont have the time to update it consistently, then its time to open your virtual doors to guest posters. Youll get the content you need, the exposure you desire, and its really [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-guest-post-submission-form/\">How to Create a Guest Post Submission Form in WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10650:\"<p>Are you interested in learning how to create a guest post submission form? Thats a great idea!</p>\n<p>If you own a blog, but dont have the time to update it consistently, then its time to open your virtual doors to guest posters. Youll get the content you need, the exposure you desire, and its really easy to get started.</p>\n<p>In this article, well show you how to create a guest post submission form for your website, step-by-step.</p>\n<h3>Choosing a Plugin for Creating a Guest Post Submission Form</h3>\n<p>Once you get your writing submission page written up, all thats left to do is give guest writers a way to submit their work. However, simply writing out your email address on your website is never a good idea. And a basic contact form wont give you the features you need to succeed.</p>\n<p>Thats why we recommend <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpforms.png\" alt=\"wpforms\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223885\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpforms.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpforms-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpforms-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>With <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a>, youll not only have the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Contact Form Plugins Compared (2018)\">best form-building tool</a> on the market, youll also have access to the special Post Submissions addon. This addon was built specifically for guest post submissions.</p>\n<p>Rather than a simple contact form that would potentially leave you sifting through junk mail in your inbox, the Post Submissions addon allows you to create a guest post submissions form with several fields designed to vet writers from the get-go.</p>\n<p>Writers can upload their drafts, which will then be saved directly on your WordPress dashboard. No more inbox clutter! You can choose whether or not to publish their pieces right from the comfort of your website.</p>\n<p>Best of all? IsItWP readers can get 10 percent off their purchase of <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> by using the coupon code <strong>SAVE10</strong>.</p>\n<p>Once you have your plugin installed and activated, follow the steps below to get started!</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Activate the Post Submissions Addon</h3>\n<p>After youve successfully activated WPForms, its time to activate the Post Submissions addon!</p>\n<p>Start by going to <strong>WPForms  Addons</strong> on your WordPress dashboard. Once on the Addons page, scroll down until you see the <strong>Post Submissions</strong> addon.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/post-submissions-addon.png\" alt=\"post submissions addon\" width=\"717\" height=\"309\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224183\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/post-submissions-addon.png 717w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/post-submissions-addon-300x129.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 717px) 100vw, 717px\" /></p>\n<p>Click <strong>Install</strong> on the addon. Once its installed, click the <strong>Activate</strong> toggle. Youll see a green Active status on the addon (shown in the pic above) when youve succeeded.</p>\n<h3>Step 2: Create a Guest Post Submission Form</h3>\n<p>Head on over to <strong>WPForms  Add New</strong> on your WordPress dashboard. Name your new form whatever youd like, and then scroll down through the templates and choose <strong>Blog Post Submission Form</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/blog-post-submisson-form.png\" alt=\"blog post submisson form\" width=\"688\" height=\"288\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224182\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/blog-post-submisson-form.png 688w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/blog-post-submisson-form-300x126.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, a form template will appear for a basic guest post submission form. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/blog-post-submission-form-template.png\" alt=\"blog post submission form template\" width=\"775\" height=\"324\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224184\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/blog-post-submission-form-template.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/blog-post-submission-form-template-300x125.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/blog-post-submission-form-template-768x321.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>This form includes 2 sections: Author Details and Create a Blog Post.</p>\n<p>Author Details includes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Name</li>\n<li>Email Address</li>\n<li>Author Bio</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And Create a Blog Post includes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Post Title</li>\n<li>Post Content</li>\n<li>Featured Image (with a file upload option)</li>\n<li>Post Excerpt</li>\n<li>Category</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you like the form as is, then feel free to click Save and move onto the next step. Or, if you want to add more fields, simply <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared (2018)\">drag and drop</a> them from the left-hand section onto your form.</p>\n<p>Personally, we recommend adding a <strong>Captcha</strong> field when you create a guest post submission form because it will ensure that bots dont send you any posts.</p>\n<p>You can find the Captcha option in the Fancy Fields section on the left-hand side. Just grab ahold of it and drag it onto your form.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/captcha-field.png\" alt=\"captcha field\" width=\"775\" height=\"325\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224185\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/captcha-field.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/captcha-field-300x126.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/captcha-field-768x322.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can also add a <strong>GDPR agreement</strong> checkbox to your form the same way. Highly recommended!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/GDPR-agreement.png\" alt=\"GDPR agreement\" width=\"775\" height=\"259\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224186\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/GDPR-agreement.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/GDPR-agreement-300x100.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/GDPR-agreement-768x257.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Finally, we also recommend saving featured image uploads in your Media Library for ease-of-use. To do this, click on the <strong>Featured Image</strong> field on your form. From there, scroll down to Advanced Options on the left-hand side and make sure the box that says <strong>Store file in WordPress Media Library</strong> is checked.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/store-to-media-library.png\" alt=\"store to media library\" width=\"278\" height=\"175\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224187\" /></p>\n<p>Once youve finished, dont forget to click <strong>Save</strong>.</p>\n<h3>Step 3: Set Up Your Post Submission Settings</h3>\n<p>While still in the WPForms editor, go to <strong>Settings  Post Submissions</strong>. From there, make sure the post submissions option is turned ON.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/post-submissions-on.png\" alt=\"post submissions on\" width=\"598\" height=\"325\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224188\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/post-submissions-on.png 598w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/post-submissions-on-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, make sure all of the dropdown menu items match the form field title found above each dropdown menu. For example, Post Title should say Post Title in the dropdown. Unless you changed or added any new fields when you were creating your form. In which case, youll need to match them up with the corresponding custom fields you created.</p>\n<p>When youve finished, click <strong>Save</strong>.</p>\n<h3>Step 4: Add Form to Your Guest Post Submissions Page</h3>\n<p>Youre nearly done! All thats left to do is add your newly-created form to your page calling for guest post submissions.</p>\n<p>From your WordPress dashboard, choose the page you want to edit. Or, go to <strong>Pages  Add New</strong> to create a new page.</p>\n<p>Once on the page you wish to add your form to, simply click on the <strong>Add Form</strong> button above your writing toolbar.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/add-form.png\" alt=\"add form\" width=\"652\" height=\"181\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224189\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/add-form.png 652w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/add-form-300x83.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 652px) 100vw, 652px\" /></p>\n<p>From there, select the form you created from the dropdown menu. Then click <strong>Add Form</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/insert-form.png\" alt=\"insert form\" width=\"392\" height=\"227\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224190\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/insert-form.png 392w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/insert-form-300x174.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 392px) 100vw, 392px\" /></p>\n<p>Thats it! Hit either Update or Publish on your page and youre all set.</p>\n<p>We hope this post helped you learn how to create a guest post submission form.</p>\n<p>If you enjoyed this tutorial, you might also like our step-by-step guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-multi-page-form-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Create a Multi-Page Form in WordPress (Step by Step)\">how to create a multi-page form in WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-guest-post-submission-form/\">How to Create a Guest Post Submission Form in WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-guest-post-submission-form/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"LiveChat Review: Is It the Best Live Chat Software?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/livechat/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/livechat/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 09 Nov 2018 18:55:04 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?post_type=isitwp_plugin&p=224270\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:581:\"<p>Do you want to add live chat to your WordPress site for instant messaging? Putting live chat on your site helps you to communicate better with your site visitors and convert more visitors into leads. To add live chat in WordPress, you can use the popular LiveChat software but is it the best choice? In [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/livechat/\">LiveChat Review: Is It the Best Live Chat Software?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20381:\"<p>Do you want to add live chat to your WordPress site for instant messaging? Putting live chat on your site helps you to communicate better with your site visitors and convert more visitors into leads. To add live chat in WordPress, you can use the popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> software but is it the best choice? </p>\n<p>In this LiveChat review, well check out how it works, its features and functionalities, pricing, and more to help you decide if its the right tool for you. </p>\n<h3>About LiveChat Software</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/live-chat.png\" alt=\"LiveChat Inc\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218486\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/live-chat.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/live-chat-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/live-chat-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> is one of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-live-chat-software-compared/\">best live chat software plugins</a> available on the market. Its an application that allows you to add live chat to your website and provide the fastest response to your users. It enables your site visitors to live chat with your team about any support and sales query. </p>\n<p>LiveChat comes with many useful chat tools such as message sneak-peek, file sharing, timeline, delivery status, and notifications. It has more interesting options to engage customers like automatic and personal greetings. Therere also feedback options to rate chat, comments, tickets, etc. </p>\n<p>The LiveChat interface is simple and easy to learn. Therere team management options like agent groups, agent roles, work scheduler, chat supervision etc. to keep your chat support team organized. It also provides reports and analytics including basic statistics, chat reports, ticket reports, daily summary and more. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> features seamless integration with 130+ tools including CMS platforms like WordPress and Drupal, eCommerce applications like Shopify and BigCommerce, and help desk applications like Knowledge Base and Zendesk. To add LiveChat on your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress website</a>, theres a free plugin in the official WordPress plugin repository. </p>\n<h3>Why You Need to Add Live Chat to Your Site?</h3>\n<p>Live chat is one of the fastest ways to respond visitors on your site. Its way faster than emails and phones. Adding live chat option on your site enables your users to ask a question as it pops up in their head. And, an instant response from your end makes communication just great!</p>\n<p>Most often, live chat is used for support and sales. If youre a company selling some products and services, youll need live chat for both support and sales. When a customer tackles a problem while using your product, they can instantly contact you via live chat. Then, you can offer an instant help. </p>\n<p>Such enhanced communication will surely enhance your impression in the users mind. And, that will definitely pay off in the long run as they share it with word of mouth and other media. For the least, theyll be your customers until youre doing the business. </p>\n<p>Live chat is great for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-compared/\">lead generation</a> and sales as you can direct a user directly to the checkout page when you know theyre interested in a product. Many users quit the idea of buying a product just because they cant find a little piece of complementary information. So, you can capture each of such users and convert them into customers. </p>\n<p>In the nutshell, live chat enhances the user experience, engagement, lead generation, and sales. Its a simple yet great way to grow your business and become successful. </p>\n<h3>LiveChat Review: Getting Started with LiveChat</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> is a premium live chat software but theyve free 30-day trial to start with. So you can sign up free and use the software free for 30 days, explore its features, and decide whether to continue with a subscription or discontinue using it. Its a great option as you can sign up free with just an email address at first. </p>\n<p>To get started, youll need to visit the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat website</a> and click <strong>Sign Up Free</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/signup-free-livechat.jpg\" alt=\"signup-free-livechat\" width=\"775\" height=\"413\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224274\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/signup-free-livechat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/signup-free-livechat-300x160.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/signup-free-livechat-768x409.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Now you should enter your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-a-free-business-email/\">business email</a> to start the LiveChat signup process. Alternatively, you can also sign up with your Google account. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-email-livechat-signup.jpg\" alt=\"enter-email-livechat-signup\" width=\"775\" height=\"387\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224275\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-email-livechat-signup.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-email-livechat-signup-300x150.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-email-livechat-signup-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Then in the second step, youll need to enter your website address. Then, also choose chat purpose. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-site-address-livechat-signup.jpg\" alt=\"enter-site-address-livechat-signup\" width=\"775\" height=\"413\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224276\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-site-address-livechat-signup.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-site-address-livechat-signup-300x160.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-site-address-livechat-signup-768x409.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>In the third and last step, you can choose an industry type, number of employees, and audience type. If youre planning to live chat only with your customers, you can check <strong>B2C</strong> only. But if you want to chat with other businesses as well, also check <strong>B2B</strong>. And, <strong>Internal Use</strong> if you want it for communication for internal use. </p>\n<p>Then click <strong>Create Account</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-account-livechat.jpg\" alt=\"create-account-livechat\" width=\"775\" height=\"499\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224277\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-account-livechat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-account-livechat-300x193.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-account-livechat-768x494.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, youll see a sign in page. Sign in with your email and password that you used in step 1. And, the signup process is complete. </p>\n<p>Then, youll see the next steps of LiveChat setup process. In the next step, youll need to install LiveChat code on your site. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-code-livechat.jpg\" alt=\"install-code-livechat\" width=\"775\" height=\"630\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224278\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-code-livechat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-code-livechat-300x244.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-code-livechat-768x624.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>For a WordPress site, its easy and safe with the LiveChat plugin. Well show you steps to installing LiveChat plugin and connecting LiveChat with WordPress in the next section below. So, you can click <strong>Ill do it later</strong> to skip to next step. </p>\n<p>In step 3, you can choose a chat theme. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/chat-theme-livechat.jpg\" alt=\"chat-theme-livechat\" width=\"775\" height=\"493\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224279\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/chat-theme-livechat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/chat-theme-livechat-300x191.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/chat-theme-livechat-768x489.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Step 4 lets you personalize your LiveChat profile. You can upload a profile photo and set a welcome message. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/personalize-livechat.jpg\" alt=\"personalize-livechat\" width=\"775\" height=\"493\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224280\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/personalize-livechat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/personalize-livechat-300x191.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/personalize-livechat-768x489.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Then finally in step 5, you can add agents to your team.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-agents-livechat.jpg\" alt=\"create-agents-livechat\" width=\"775\" height=\"493\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224281\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-agents-livechat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-agents-livechat-300x191.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-agents-livechat-768x489.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>After adding the total number of agents, you can click <strong>Go to Application</strong> button. </p>\n<p>Now, youll see LiveChat interface open. There youll see a notification at the top that you havent installed LiveChat on your site. Now, well show you how to install it on your site. </p>\n<h3>Installing LiveChat on Your WordPress Site</h3>\n<p>Once youve completed LiveChat setup process, youre now ready to install it on your WordPress site. Its a simple process of connecting your LiveChat account with your WordPress site. Theres a free LiveChat plugin for WordPress for this purpose.  </p>\n<p>To start with, login to your WordPress dashboard and visit <strong>Plugins &raquo; Add New</strong>. Type <strong>LiveChat</strong> in the search box first. Once it appears, install and activate it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-livechat-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"install-livechat-plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"426\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224282\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-livechat-plugin.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-livechat-plugin-300x165.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-livechat-plugin-768x422.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>After its activated, you can see <strong>LiveChat</strong> menu added to your dashboard panel. Go to <strong>LiveChat &raquo; Settings</strong>. </p>\n<p>Next, youll need to click <strong>Sign in with LiveChat</strong> button to connect LiveChat with WordPress. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/connect-livechat-with-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"connect-livechat-with-wordpress\" width=\"775\" height=\"411\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224283\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/connect-livechat-with-wordpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/connect-livechat-with-wordpress-300x159.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/connect-livechat-with-wordpress-768x407.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>After that, youll see your WordPress site connected with LiveChat. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-installed-in-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"livechat-installed-in-wordpress\" width=\"775\" height=\"343\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224284\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-installed-in-wordpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-installed-in-wordpress-300x133.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-installed-in-wordpress-768x340.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Click on the <strong>Open web application</strong> to go to the LiveChat interface. </p>\n<p>Now you can manage your chats, chat team, and everything from there. </p>\n<p>If you check your website, youll see LiveChat screen added to your site.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-added-on-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"livechat-added-on-wordpress\" width=\"385\" height=\"558\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224291\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-added-on-wordpress.jpg 385w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-added-on-wordpress-207x300.jpg 207w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 385px) 100vw, 385px\" /></p>\n<h3>Checking out LiveChat Features</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> is a feature-rich application for adding live chat to your site. It has plenty of chat tools, customization options, and team management features. </p>\n<p><strong>1. Simple yet complete chat screen</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-chat-screen.jpg\" alt=\"livechat-chat-screen\" width=\"775\" height=\"478\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224285\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-chat-screen.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-chat-screen-300x185.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-chat-screen-768x474.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can see the list of chats, chat box, and customers contact info at the same screen. It makes it easy to manage all chats at once based on the priority. </p>\n<p><strong>2. Comprehensive Chat Reports</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-reports.jpg\" alt=\"livechat-reports\" width=\"775\" height=\"489\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224286\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-reports.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-reports-300x189.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-reports-768x485.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> provides highly comprehensive reports where you can see stats for chats, tickets, and eCommerce. </p>\n<p><strong>Full Customization Made Possible</strong> </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-settings.jpg\" alt=\"livechat-settings\" width=\"775\" height=\"489\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224287\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-settings-300x189.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-settings-768x485.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> allows you to fully customize how your chat interface looks like and how it works. You can customize anything by going to the <strong>Settings</strong> menu in your LiveChat account.</p>\n<h3>LiveChat Software: Pricing and Support</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> is a premium live chat software however you can always start with their 30-days free trial. </p>\n<p>If youre satisfied with its features after 30 days, you can subscribe to one of their plans. Therere 4 pricing plans available. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-pricing.jpg\" alt=\"livechat-pricing\" width=\"775\" height=\"518\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224288\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-pricing.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-pricing-300x201.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-pricing-768x513.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The basic LiveChat plan is <strong>Starter</strong>. Its suitable for small office or home office needs. You can create unlimited agent accounts but it allows only 60-day chat history and basic chat customization. If you need unlimited chat history and full chat customization, youll need to buy <strong>team</strong> plan at least. </p>\n<p>The Starter costs $16 monthly per logged in agent. </p>\n<p>Second, <strong>Team</strong> plan is for a full-time support team. It allows you to create unlimited agent accounts, see unlimited chat history, full chat customization, and basic reporting. It costs $33 monthly per logged in agent. </p>\n<p>Third, <strong>Business</strong> plan is the most popular plan. Its suitable for bigger firms to organize customer service department. It has more additional advanced features than the Team plan like work scheduler, staffing prediction, etc. It costs $50 monthly per logged in agent. </p>\n<p>The highest priced LiveChat plan is called <strong>Enterprise</strong>. It has the most advanced features. Its designed for Fortune 500 companies or alike. It costs $149 monthly per logged in agent. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> provides 24/4 dedicated support via live chat. Plus, it has a rich knowledgebase with tutorials, webinars, etc. to help you with any problem you tackle while using this software. </p>\n<h3>Our Verdict on Using LiveChat Software on Your WordPress Site</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> is undoubtedly a great chat tool suitable for all level users. Its useful for small businesses as well as big Fortune 500 companies. </p>\n<p>Using LiveChat is easy. It has simple user interface, yet powerful features to run live chat on your website efficiently. Installing LiveChat on WordPress is easy with their free plugin as you dont need to touch a single piece of code to install and use. </p>\n<p>We believe that <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> is the perfect live chat software for adding live chat to your WordPress site. It has a complete set of features youll ever need to run live chat. Its integration with eCommerce and other tools makes your life just easy. </p>\n<p>We give it 4.5 out of 5 stars. Heres the breakdown of our review score: </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/livechat/\">LiveChat Review: Is It the Best Live Chat Software?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/livechat/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"24 Best WordPress Education Themes (Compared)  2018\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-education-themes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-education-themes/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 08 Nov 2018 10:01:23 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"best wordpress themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"education themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"premium themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=223651\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:646:\"<p>Are you looking for the best education themes for WordPress? Whether youre in charge of a schools website or selling your own courses out of your home, youll need the perfect theme to captivate your students. The right theme can help convert visitors into students, showcase your courses, enhance your professional credibility, and skyrocket your [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-education-themes/\">24 Best WordPress Education Themes (Compared) &#8211; 2018</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30621:\"<p>Are you looking for the best education themes for WordPress? Whether youre in charge of a schools website or selling your own courses out of your home, youll need the perfect theme to captivate your students. The right theme can help convert visitors into students, showcase your courses, enhance your professional credibility, and skyrocket your online success.</p>\n<p>In this article, well share the 24 best WordPress education themes on the market. Theyre all responsive, so any theme you choose from this list will look fantastic on any device.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-motive/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Motive</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-motive/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Motive.jpg\" alt=\"Motive\" width=\"775\" height=\"230\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223747\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Motive.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Motive-300x89.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Motive-768x228.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Packed with easy-to-use shortcodes, the Motive theme is eye-catching and modern. Using grid, masonry, or mosaic layouts, you can showcase your educational portfolio effortlessly.</p>\n<p>Powered by the ever-popular Tesla Framework, Motive features parallax backgrounds, custom post types, featured images, featured videos, custom widgets, its own form builder, and more.</p>\n<p>Its highly customizable and you can tweak it endlessly until you get it looking exactly how you want it. Or, if youre in a rush, you can import one of their pre-built demo sites and simply change the content to your own.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-motive/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Motive Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-academia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Academia Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-academia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/academia-pro.png\" alt=\"academia pro\" width=\"550\" height=\"274\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223748\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/academia-pro.png 550w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/academia-pro-300x149.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Flexibility is the name of the game with Academia Pro. You can use a 3 column layout or a 2 column layout. And you can put your sidebar on either the left or right side. Plus, you can change the layout of each page individually; meaning, you can have a 3 column layout on one page and a 2 column layout on another!</p>\n<p>The header comes with 3 menu options. You can use all of them or none of them. Personally, we like the menu option that comes with an eye-catching call-to-action button!</p>\n<p>You can also use your own, custom logo for your header image. Academia Pro is perfect for schools, or home educators whove developed their own brand.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-academia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Academia Pro Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-elms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Elms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-elms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elms.jpg\" alt=\"elms\" width=\"773\" height=\"324\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223749\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elms.jpg 773w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elms-300x126.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/upl