uring a blog or an online shop.</p>\n<p>Import any of the dozens of pre-built layouts, or utilize the intuitive drag and drop builder, and get your site started immediately.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Presence Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-lenscap/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">16. Lenscap</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-lenscap/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/lenscap-hero-1.jpg\" alt=\"lenscap\" width=\"772\" height=\"317\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223762\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/lenscap-hero-1.jpg 772w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/lenscap-hero-1-300x123.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/lenscap-hero-1-768x315.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p>With a sophisticated layout and beautiful typography, Lenscap is amazing for educators looking to showcase their services via photos and videos. Were in love with the customizable content carousel!</p>\n<p>It also includes multiple color schemes, making it simple to match your site with your brand.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-lenscap/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Lenscap Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cyberchimps-edupro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">17. Edu Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cyberchimps-edupro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edupro.jpg\" alt=\"edupro\" width=\"772\" height=\"327\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223764\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edupro.jpg 772w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edupro-300x127.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edupro-768x325.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The welcome image, with an eye-catching call-to-action button, is the crown jewel of this theme. Edu Pro was designed to increase your conversions and help you generate traffic to your most valued landing pages.</p>\n<p>Effortlessly showcase seminars, courses, training videos, and services with its pre-built layouts. You can also get visitors to sign up to your newsletter thanks to its integration with many of the most popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-email-marketing-services-compared/\" title=\"9 Best Email Marketing Services Compared\">email marketing services</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cyberchimps-edupro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Edu Pro Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-monochrome/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">18. Monochrome</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-monochrome/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/monochrome-pro.jpg\" alt=\"monochrome\" width=\"775\" height=\"331\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223765\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/monochrome-pro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/monochrome-pro-300x128.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/monochrome-pro-768x328.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Simple-yet-substantial, Monochrome was designed by the fine folks at StudioPress and utilizes their famous Genesis framework.</p>\n<p>Making great use of white space, Monochrome is a master of minimal. Your educational website will look distinct, confident, and utterly professional.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-monochrome/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Monochrome Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-neuton/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">19. Neuton</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-neuton/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/neuton.jpg\" alt=\"neuton\" width=\"775\" height=\"385\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223766\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/neuton.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/neuton-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/neuton-768x382.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>A magazine-style layout that stands out from the crowd with its trending topics feature, Neuton is perfect if youre looking for something truly unique.</p>\n<p>Highly customizable, Neuton features a variety of custom widgets and multiple color schemes. You can even assign a different color scheme for each page you create!</p>\n<p>Dont feel like customizing your site from scratch? No problem. Neuton includes a 1-click demo installer so you can get started immediately.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-neuton/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Neuton Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-education-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">20. Education Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-education-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pro.jpg\" alt=\"education pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"367\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223767\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pro-300x142.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pro-768x364.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Education Pro is for institutions who have a great deal of content to share. This theme is perfect for showcasing text, video, and audio posts.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-education-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Education Pro Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-wp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">21. Education WP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-wp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-wp.png\" alt=\"education wp\" width=\"772\" height=\"361\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223768\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-wp.png 772w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-wp-300x140.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-wp-768x359.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Complete with its own LMS, Education WP is quick to set up thanks to over 14 pre-built demo sites you can install. Or, if you feel like building your site from scratch, you can use WPBakery or SiteOrigins drag and drop builders.</p>\n<p>Designed to be a multilingual site, this theme is WooCommerce ready and performance optimized.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-wp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Education WP Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/eikra-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">22. Eikra Education</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/eikra-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Eikra-Education.png\" alt=\"Eikra Education\" width=\"774\" height=\"306\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223769\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Eikra-Education.png 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Eikra-Education-300x119.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Eikra-Education-768x304.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This contemporary theme is great for a variety of education centers. It comes with the LearnPress LMS plugin, so youll have all the features you need to create powerful online courses.</p>\n<p>You can get started quickly with Eikra Education thanks to its 1-click demo import. Or, you can build your site from scratch using WPBakery, the included drag and drop builder.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/eikra-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Eikra Education Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/edugate-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">23. Edugate Education</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/edugate-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edugate.png\" alt=\"edugate\" width=\"774\" height=\"335\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223770\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edugate.png 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edugate-300x130.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edugate-768x332.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Edugate Education recommends using its theme for schools, libraries, and training centers. Its also perfect for home educators and private tutors.</p>\n<p>Its a modern theme with a creative flair, perfect for enticing new students.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/edugate-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Edugate Education Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">24. Education Pack</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pack.png\" alt=\"education pack\" width=\"775\" height=\"341\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223771\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pack.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pack-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pack-768x338.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As you might expect from the name, Education Pack comes with a pack of education site demos that you can easily install to get your website up-and-running. These demos include sites for driving schools, dance academies, design schools, and more!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Education Pack Today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the best WordPress Education themes.</p>\n<p>If you found this post useful, you might also enjoy our article on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-lms-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress LMS Plugins Compared (2018)\">best Learning Management System plugins</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-education-themes/\">24 Best WordPress Education Themes (Compared) &#8211; 2018</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-education-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"dat